<br>
2) sarnac emblazoned tabard 14 ac, 10 MR, maybe 100pp....Dwarven Ringmail also fits here.<br>
<br>
3) 7 MR bracers.  Darn cheap, especially if you know the enchanter...perhaps 100 for 2 sounds about right.  I think i paid 150 about a year ago.<br>
<br>
4) Blackened Iron Crown 5 MR/and damn near all others (could get this in a good runneye group, or just buy for a couple 100)<br>
<br>
5) Whenever you get a chance, beg a mage for a Dagger of Summoning (5mr...5/19 weapon...toss it in your ranged slot, maybe offhand too if pking a caster)<br>
<br>
6) cost starts to go up here, as you now must upgrade the armors you have for pieces that MR or other desired resistances.  Ravenscale gloves are an example...couple mr...your CLASS glove, and decent gear if you are a main char for many lvls.<br>
<br>
7) Gaurdian Sword from Skyshrine-no drop, and a 9/25 weapon with 3 MR i believe...have a friend grab one, or get one yourself in time.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Runed Bone Fork-10 MR/FR/CR...probably out of the question for the now, but a good day trader can get all this stuff in little time at all.<br>
